  "remediation": "<p><strong>To let administrators set passwords for users</strong></p> <ol> <li dir=\"ltr\">In&nbsp;<a href=\"https://support.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/4581766374554#topic_hfg_dyz_1hb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Admin Center</a>, click <strong>Account</strong>&nbsp;in the sidebar, then select&nbsp;<strong>Security &gt; Advanced</strong>.</li> <li>On the&nbsp;<strong>Passwords</strong> tab, verify <strong>Enable admins to set passwords </strong>is<strong> not selected</strong>. <p><strong>You must be the account owner to see this setting.</strong></p> </li> <li>Click&nbsp;<strong>Save</strong>.</li> </ol>",
